---
title: Double Caribbean Jerk Prawns & Veggie Couscous with Baby Leaves & Mayonnaise
description: The couscous is so fluffy that it’s cuddling the fresh prawns in a warm hug. Let those flavours embrace you with Caribbean jerk
seasoning and veggies, then finish off this vibrant and refreshing dinner with a creamy drizzle of mayo.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
